                    "body": "5.2.9 on all three servers that I've tested.  The PHP packages were provided by dotdeb.org (the server that produced the segfault had the 5.2.9-0.dotdeb.2 packages installed).",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alexadriaanse",
